WEBVTT

00:00.020 --> 00:02.493
<i>- Previously on "The Family"...</i>
- Eyes on the prize, champ.

00:02.660 --> 00:03.559
- Ah!
- [Gasps]

00:03.594 --> 00:05.780
How did you know
this is the one I wanted?

00:05.860 --> 00:07.258
I know you, Cruz.

00:07.293 --> 00:08.960
Say hi to your boyfriend for me.

00:14.200 --> 00:15.166
So what are we looking at?

00:15.201 --> 00:16.434
Every night he gets on a bus

00:16.470 --> 00:18.135
and goes somewhere in this neighborhood.

00:18.712 --> 00:20.338
Who the hell is he seeing at 2:00 a.m.?

00:21.842 --> 00:23.174
I think you may be in danger.

00:23.209 --> 00:24.708
You think Doug took that boy?

00:24.744 --> 00:26.810
- We'll talk in the car.
- Let me get my purse.

00:26.846 --> 00:28.044
Aah!

00:28.080 --> 00:31.615
Man: <i>...after a series
of decade-old graphic texts</i>

00:31.650 --> 00:33.927
<i>- emerged earlier today,
- What?</i>

00:33.952 --> 00:34.818
<i>romantically linking...</i>

00:34.854 --> 00:36.987
<i>...Warren's husband to Nina Meyer...</i>

00:37.022 --> 00:38.489
Claire: What did you do?

00:38.524 --> 00:39.723
Is his name Ben?

00:39.759 --> 00:41.824
No, it's not him!
It is not your brother!

00:41.860 --> 00:44.059
- Mom, please.
- I am not your mom.

00:44.095 --> 00:46.462
Monkey survived his spin in the dryer.

00:52.169 --> 00:53.703
Thanks for coming by.

00:53.738 --> 00:55.364
I know it's been a while.

00:56.186 --> 00:57.806
I stand by my work.

00:59.410 --> 01:02.160
Gabe: <i>Well, kid, here we are...</i>

01:03.140 --> 01:04.105
<i>in the suck.</i>

01:04.140 --> 01:08.483
<i>I was pretty pumped
to solve that case with you,</i>

01:08.519 --> 01:11.635
<i>but where I am now,
I won't be much help.</i>

01:17.960 --> 01:18.992
[Ringing]

01:19.028 --> 01:22.651
<i>Good news is,
you know more than you think.</i>

01:22.686 --> 01:25.677
[Ringing]

01:25.713 --> 01:29.583
[Cellphone rings]

01:29.684 --> 01:32.184
<i>You know they'll get rid
of the evidence first.</i>

01:35.256 --> 01:37.848
<i>You know they're probably
hiding in plain sight.</i>

01:43.264 --> 01:46.999
Oh! [Breathing heavily]

01:47.035 --> 01:49.996
<i>Bad news is, you don't know
the most important thing.</i>

01:50.389 --> 01:52.378
Gabe on voicemail: <i>It's Clements.
Call you back.</i>

01:52.403 --> 01:53.060
[Beep]

01:53.085 --> 01:55.275
Get out of bed and come to work, would
you?

01:56.865 --> 01:58.282
Gabe: <i>I'm already gone.</i>

